choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: interior_minister_party != "BBWR"
on-arrival: leverage -= 5; interior_minister_party = "BBWR"; interior_minister = "Severing"
go-to: ministries

Carl Severing of the BBWR has been appointed Interior Minister.

